               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291203-19-cd101" type="crimeDate">27th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291203-19-off100 t18291203-19-cd101"></join>, 18 yards of ribbon, value 8s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18291203-19-victim229" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Hall
               <interp inst="t18291203-19-victim229" type="surname" value="Hall"></interp>
